While athletes and fans enthusiastically represent their countries in the World Cup, the Coursera Cup encourages our global community to represent their country or region via their power of learning. To influence your country/region Coursera Cup ranking, invite friends from your country and watch lecture videos during the 2014 World Cup. <a href="http://blog.coursera.org/post/90472363862/coursera-cup-week-2-leaderboard-update" target="_blank">Week 2 Leaderboard Standings</a>
</p><h2>COURSERA CUP LEADERBOARD STANDINGS</h2>
<p>
The Coursera Cup Leaderboard is a measurement of the most active Courserians per capita per country/region with over 10k learners. We are measuring &#8220;Activity&#8221; by video lectures watched and number of learners per capita:
